#: dashboard/views.py:437
msgid "Transporte Público"
msgstr "Public Transport"

#: dashboard/views.py:439
msgid ""
"¡Bien hecho! Ha plantado 13 árboles, con esto has logrado contrarrestar el "
"CO2 al usar transporte publico. obtuviste tu primera insignia. ¡Sigue así y "
"ayuda a hacer del mundo un lugar más verde y saludable!"
msgstr ""
"Well done! You've planted 13 trees, and by doing so, you've managed to "
"counteract theCO2 from using public transportation. You've earned your first "
"badge. Keep it up andhelp make the world a greener and healthier place!"

#: dashboard/views.py:442
msgid "Automovil"
msgstr "Car"

#: dashboard/views.py:444
msgid ""
"¡Felicidades! con la siembra de 76 arboles lograste capturar el CO2 que "
"genera un carro. Sigue así y pronto tendrás tu segunda insignia."
msgstr ""
"Congratulations! with the planting of 76 trees you managed to capture the "
"CO2 generated by one car. Keep it up and soon you will have your second "
"badge."

#: dashboard/views.py:446
msgid "Moto"
msgstr "Motorcycle"

#: dashboard/views.py:448
msgid ""
"¡Muy bien! Has plantado 10 árboles mas y lograste capturar el equivalente de "
"emisión de CO2 de una Moto, Continúa cuidando de ellos, pronto obtendrás mas "
"insignias."
msgstr ""
"Very well done! You have planted 10 more trees and managed to capture the "
"equivalent  CO2 emission of a Motorcycle, Continue taking care of them, soon "
"you will get more badges"

#: dashboard/views.py:451
msgid "Avión"
msgstr "Aircraft"

#: dashboard/views.py:453
msgid ""
"¡Eres un verdadero héroe del medio ambiente! Has plantado más de 100 árboles "
"y con eso estas contrarrestado en CO2 que produce un avión. Tu dedicación "
"para combatir el cambio climático y proteger nuestro planeta es inspiradora. "
"¡Sigue así!"
msgstr ""
"You are a true environmental hero! You have planted more than 100 trees and "
"with that you are offsetting the CO2 produced by an airplane. Your "
"dedication to fighting climate change and protecting our planet is inspiring."
"Keep it up!"

